&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-a-new-post&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;markdownIt-Anchor&#34; href=&#34;#create-a-new-post&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Create a new post&lt;/h3&gt;
